    {
      "parameters": {
        "jsCode": "const item = $input.first();\nconst fullName = (item.json['Full Name'] || '').trim();\n\n// Extract first name, handle \"Dr.\" prefix\nconst nameParts = fullName.split(/\\s+/);\nlet firstName = nameParts[0] || fullName;\nif (['dr.', 'dr', 'doctor'].includes(firstName.toLowerCase()) && nameParts.length > 1) {\n  firstName = nameParts[1];\n}\n\nconst htmlBody = `<div style='font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif;font-size:16px;line-height:1.4;color:#000;'>\n\n<p style='margin:0 0 30px 0;'>Hi ${firstName},</p>\n\n<p style='margin:0 0 16px 0;'>\nI noticed you're hiring for a front desk receptionist. This might be useful either way.\n</p>\n\n<p style='margin:0 0 16px 0;'>\nEven great receptionists can't answer calls during lunch, after hours, or when they're with a patient at the desk.\nThose missed calls? Often new patients who just call the next clinic on Google.\n</p>\n\n<p style='margin:0 0 12px 0;'>\nI built an <strong style='font-weight:700;'>AI Receptionist for dental practices</strong> that acts as a safety net. It:\n</p>\n\n<ul style='margin:0 0 16px 20px;padding-left:20px;'>\n  <li style='margin-bottom:8px;'><strong style='font-weight:700;'>Answers calls 24/7</strong> \\u2013 nights, weekends, holidays</li>\n  <li style='margin-bottom:8px;'>Books, reschedules, and cancels appointments during the conversation</li>\n  <li style='margin-bottom:8px;'>Answers questions about services, hours, and insurance</li>\n  <li>Logs every call in a dashboard with full details</li>\n</ul>\n\n<p style='margin:0 0 16px 0;'>\nIt works alongside your team, not instead of them.\n</p>\n\n<p style='margin:0 0 16px 0;'>\n<strong style='font-weight:700;'>I recorded a 90-second demo</strong> of it handling a patient trying to book an appointment.\nWant me to send it?\n</p>\n\n<p style='margin:0 0 16px 0;'>\nJust reply <strong style='font-weight:700;'>\"DEMO\"</strong> and I'll share the link.\n</p>\n\n<p style='margin:16px 0 0 0;'>\nBest,<br>\nMoiz<br>\nFounder \\u2013 OrthoAI<br>\nAI Dental Receptionist\n</p>\n\n</div>`;\n\nreturn [{\n  json: {\n    recipientEmail: item.json['Email'],\n    fullName: fullName,\n    firstName: firstName,\n    emailBody: htmlBody\n  }\n}];"
      },
